{"title":"The 2026 Brooks Open Factory! Get Your (Free) Tickets Now","link":"https://theradavist.com/2026-brooks-open-factory","date":1777276338000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-98.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-98.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-98.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-98.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>On 18 July 2026, the legendary Birmingham, UK-based saddle manufacturer <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/brooks-england\" target=\"_blank\">Brooks England</a> will once again open its factory doors to the public for a celebration of manufacturing history. Tickets (which are free, but limited) are available now. Sign up at <a href=\"https://www.brooksengland.com/open-factory-2026\" target=\"_blank\">Brooks England</a> to ensure you don’t miss out on this marvelous opportunity…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-106.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-106.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-106.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-106.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>After <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/brooks-england-open-factory\" target=\"_blank\">a successful first edition of the Open Factory in 2025</a>, the appetite for opportunities like this was immediately apparent. On a guided tour of the floor, you’ll meet the people who bring the factory to life each day, and witness in action the tools, machines, and hands that turn raw material into a saddle shaped by you, mile after mile.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-94.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-94.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-94.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-94.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-85.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-85.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-85.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-85.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Alongside the tours, we’ll be welcoming some of our favorite brands to the factory courtyard. There’ll be food &amp; drink, and space to chat, compare builds, and debate whether 650b was a good idea after all.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-61.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-61.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-61.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-61.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-47.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-47.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-47.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-47.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-35.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-35.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-35.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/07/2025_Brooks_Open_Factory-35.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Whether you’re a lifelong rider, a fan of manufacturing past and present, or just factory-curious, we’d love to have you here in Smethwick. Hundreds attended the inaugural event and went away smiling – so don’t miss your chance to come see what’s behind it all.</p>\n<p>Get your tickets for the Brooks Open Factory now at <a href=\"https://www.brooksengland.com/open-factory-2026\" target=\"_blank\">Brooks England</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2026-brooks-open-factory\">The 2026 Brooks Open Factory! Get Your (Free) Tickets Now</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"735452f72892600dc45ee518c16e8e217e1557ca31150b9974bfc5f6409abc63","category":"Cycling"}